Allows the SIP program to use I2C IO extender boards based on the mcp23017 Chip.

This is a 16-BIT I2C expander chip.

Written by niffum

Requirements: I2C must be enabled on the Raspberry PI and smbus lib must be installed 

##### List all plugin files below preceded by a blank line [file_name.ext path] relative to SIP directory #####

mcp23017.py plugins
mcp23017.html templates
mcp23017-docs.html static/docs/plugins
mcp23017.json data (generated)
mcp23017.manifest plugins/manifests

